<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		#parse("header.vm")		
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container_12">
			<div class="grid_12 header">
				<h2>Daily Email Service</h2>
			</div>
            <div class="grid_2">
                <nav>
                    <ul>
                        <li id="yourhere"><a href=#springUrl("/index")>Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href=#springUrl("/login")>Login</a></li>
                        <li><a href=#springUrl("/register")>Register</a></li>                        
                        
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="grid_7 content">
                <p>This daily email service allows you to choose various weather
                    and news options.  Specifically, you can receive current 
                    temperature information and weather forecast data.  Currently,
                    you can get 5 articles from WSJ, NYT, and/or Richmond TD.</p>
            </div>
			<div class="grid_3">
				<div class="error">
				#if($exception)
					#springMessageText($exception.code $exception.message)
				#end					
				</div>
				<form name="login" action=#springUrl("/login/index") method="post">
					<label>E-Mail Address:</label>
					<input type="text" name="emailAddress" />
					<label>Password:</label> 
					<input type="password" name="pwd" />
					<input type="submit" value="Login" />
				</form>
            </div>
             <div class="grid_12 footer">
            Nate Paulus Copyright &copy; 2012
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
